{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe the whole-- they're, they're mellowed because someone said the gassing had stopped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you know, the ghost of winter was going to-- winter, 19-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 44- 45.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what, you know, is that it was clear that Germany was going to lose the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were already preparing in their mind for escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And why should they load themselves more than they already had on their, on their, sort of, conscience-- if they had a conscience.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whether the gas chambers were working with the new transport, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But these people who were selected I'm sure went into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, this was our conversation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Unless I can think of something else during that time-- yeah, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Oh, no, I'll make it short.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was once an incident that I, the men, the German civilians, stood behind me and made fun of my drawings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, you're not the German sort of pun, where you said you are not a, a, a-- maler is, to mal is paint and also grinding with a miller, you know, those, you know, grinding or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said you're not a maler, a painter, but you are a maler, sort of meaning the others of the mill.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And of course I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I proved and he was quite happy with me in the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was only the other incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One more, perhaps, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Where others were very, very cold in the last days in Auschwitz and working in the streets and had-- and hungry and dying, I was in a very small room, away from my father who also had an easy job, painting some letters on some electrical sort of boxes.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
